TITLE: Deleting Contact in Intercom with TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to delete a single contact from Intercom by providing the contact_id to the delete method.
SOURCE: https://github.com/intercom/intercom-node/blob/master/reference.md#_snippet_33

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
await client.contacts.delete({
    contact_id: "contact_id",
});
```

