TITLE: Tagging a Contact with Intercom API in Typescript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to tag a specific contact with a tag in Intercom workspace using Intercom Node client. It returns the updated `Tag` object. It requires a `contact_id` and a tag `id` to identify the contact and tag respectively.
SOURCE: https://github.com/intercom/intercom-node/blob/master/reference.md#_snippet_44

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
await client.tags.tagContact({
    contact_id: "63a07ddf05a32042dffac965",
    id: "7522907",
});
```

