TITLE: Listing Attached Contacts for a Company with Intercom Node SDK (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates retrieving the list of all contacts attached to a specific company. Requires the Intercom client and 'Intercom.ListAttachedContactsRequest' containing the target 'company_id'. The output is a CompanyAttachedContacts object with the set of associated contacts. This operation is useful for managing company-contact relationships and requires appropriate permissions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/intercom/intercom-node/blob/master/reference.md#_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
await client.companies.listAttachedContacts({
    company_id: "5f4d3c1c-7b1b-4d7d-a97e-6095715c6632",
});
```

----------------------------------------

TITLE: Retrieving Ticket Details Using TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Illustrates how to fetch details of a specific ticket by its ID. Utilizes the 'client.tickets.get' method with request options specifying the ticket ID.
SOURCE: https://github.com/intercom/intercom-node/blob/master/reference.md#_snippet_91

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
await client.tickets.get({
    ticket_id: "ticket_id",
});
```

