TITLE: Updating an Article in Intercom API
DESCRIPTION: This function updates the details of a single article using the `client.articles.update()` method.  Requires the `article_id` and the fields to be updated, such as title and body. The output is an Intercom.Article object.
SOURCE: https://github.com/intercom/intercom-node/blob/master/reference.md#_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
await client.articles.update({
    article_id: "123",
    title: "Christmas is here!",
    body: "<p>New gifts in store for the jolly season</p>",
});
```

