TITLE: Creating a Ticket Type Attribute in Intercom Node.js SDK with TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Creates a new attribute associated with a ticket type using specified parameters including ticket_type_id, attribute name, description, data type, and required status. Returns the created ticket type attribute object. Requires the Intercom client with proper authentication and the appropriate request structure.
SOURCE: https://github.com/intercom/intercom-node/blob/master/reference.md#_snippet_111

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
await client.ticketTypes.attributes.create({
    ticket_type_id: "ticket_type_id",
    name: "Attribute Title",
    description: "Attribute Description",
    data_type: "string",
    required_to_create: false,
});
```

